latestPosts.caption:
Shade matching tip: Always swatch your perfect matched foundation on your hand before going to buy new foundations. And after swatching new shades- leave them on for atleast 5mins before you buy to ensure they don’t oxidise. 

Why do I almost always get share matched wrong at beauty counters🥲 Either it’s too white or too yellow!
